               <p>The prosecutor is a <rs id="t17501205-25-viclabel131" type="occupation">Dutchman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17501205-25-victim227 t17501205-25-viclabel131"></join>; he was going thro' <placeName id="t17501205-25-crimeloc132">Bishopsgate</placeName>
